data.title: Bald Eagle Mountain in Wasatch County UT (Heber City Area)
data.meta_description: See the FREE map and info about Bald Eagle Mountain in Wasatch County, UT. Bald Eagle Mountain is a Summits on the Utah Topo Map called Heber City.
data.text: Map and location information for Bald Eagle Mountain in Utah: Bald Eagle Mountain is one of the Summits in Wasatch County, UT and can be found on the Heber City USGS topographic quad map. The GPS coordinates are 40.6235629 (latitude), -111.4815821 (longitude) and the approximate elevation is 8,471 feet (2,582 meters) above sea level. Have you been to Utah's Bald Eagle Mountain before? If so, we ask that you post a quick review of it below. Tell us the time of year, what your goal was, and how your trip went. Thanks for sharing your experience at Bald Eagle Mountain!
